'''''Fâ Chhiên-kut''''' ({{lang-en|'''''The Journey of Flower'''''}}) he kói-phiên chhṳ [[Fresh Kó-kó]] ke hièn-fam séu-sot ''Siên-hia̍p Khì-yèn chṳ̂ Fâ Chhiên-kut'', yî 2014-ngièn 5-ngie̍t 6-ngit chhai Kóng-sî khôi-kî, 9-ngie̍t sat-chhiâng<ref>[http://www.4hw.com.cn/yule/dalu/30847.html    《花千骨》今日开拍赵丽颖出演花千骨 霍建华版白子画《女医明妃传》后进组]</ref><ref>[http://ent.sina.com.cn/v/m/2014-05-07/11394137669.shtml 《花千骨》开机 霍建华赵丽颖演凄美爱情]</ref>. Chú-yeu kóng-su̍t Fâ Chhiên-kut lâu Pha̍k Chṳ́-va̍k sṳ̂-thù ke sṳ̀n-siên lâu oi-chhìn ku-sṳ .
